SELECT /* CASE WHEN ( A.TRANS_FLAG1 != 'N' ) THEN '2' -- NEW (IPWON) WHEN ( A.TRANS_FLAG2 != 'N' ) THEN '9' -- TOIWON WHEN ( A.TRANS_FLAG3 != 'N' ) THEN '8' -- TRANS ROOM WHEN ( A.TRANS_FLAG4 != 'N' ) THEN '7' -- TRANS NUT ELSE '0' -- NONE CHANGE END AS TRANS_YN */ CASE WHEN ( A.TRANS_FLAG1 != 'N') THEN '1' ELSE '0' END IP , CASE WHEN ( A.TRANS_FLAG2 != 'N') THEN '1' ELSE '0' END TI , CASE WHEN ( A.TRANS_FLAG3 != 'N') THEN '1' ELSE '0' END TN , CASE WHEN ( A.TRANS_FLAG4 != 'N') THEN '1' ELSE '0' END TR , '0' CA -- , A.HOSP_CODE AS HOSP_CODE , A.BUNHO AS BUNHO , A0.SUNAME AS SUNAME -- , A.NUT_DATE AS NUT_DATE , A.BLD_GUBUN AS BLD_GUBUN -- , A.HO_DONG AS TO_HO_DONG , A.HO_CODE AS TO_HO_CODE -- , N0.NUR_SO_NAME AS TO_DIRECT_CODE_D , N1.NUR_SO_NAME AS TO_DIRECT_CODE1_D , N2.NUR_SO_NAME AS TO_DIRECT_CODE2_D , N3.NUR_SO_NAME AS TO_DIRECT_CODE3_D , N4.NUR_SO_NAME AS TO_NOMIMONO , CASE WHEN ( A.BLD_GUBUN = '1' ) THEN A.JO_KUMJISIK WHEN ( A.BLD_GUBUN = '2' ) THEN A.JU_KUMJISIK WHEN ( A.BLD_GUBUN = '3' ) THEN A.SEOK_KUMJISIK ELSE NULL END AS TO_KUMJISIK -- , TO_CHAR(B.NUT_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AS FROM_NUT_DATE , B.BLD_GUBUN AS FROM_BLD_GUBUN -- , B.HO_DONG FROM_HO_DONG , B.HO_CODE FROM_HO_CODE -- , N02.NUR_SO_NAME AS FROM_DIRECT_CODE_D , N12.NUR_SO_NAME AS FROM_DIRECT_CODE1_D , N22.NUR_SO_NAME AS FROM_DIRECT_CODE2_D , N32.NUR_SO_NAME AS FROM_DIRECT_CODE3_D , N42.NUR_SO_NAME AS FROM_NOMIMONO , CASE WHEN ( A.BLD_GUBUN = '1' ) THEN B.JO_KUMJISIK WHEN ( A.BLD_GUBUN = '2' ) THEN B.JU_KUMJISIK WHEN ( A.BLD_GUBUN = '3' ) THEN B.SEOK_KUMJISIK ELSE NULL END AS FROM_KUMJISIK -- --, A.* --, B.* FROM NUT2010 A , ( SELECT B.* FROM ( SELECT A.* FROM ( SELECT A.* FROM NUT2011 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.MAGAM_KEY < ( SELECT Z.MAGAM_KEY FROM NUT2011 Z WHERE Z.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND Z.NUT_DATE = :f_nut_date AND Z.BLD_GUBUN = :f_bld_gubun AND Z.MAGAM_SEQ = :f_magam_seq ) ORDER BY A.HOSP_CODE, A.MAGAM_KEY DESC ) A WHERE ROWNUM < 2 ) A , NUT2010 B WHERE B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.NUT_DATE = A.NUT_DATE AND B.BLD_GUBUN = A.BLD_GUBUN AND B.MAGAM_SEQ = A.MAGAM_SEQ ) B -- , OUT0101 A0 -- , NUR0112 N0 , NUR0112 N1 , NUR0112 N2 , NUR0112 N3 , NUR0112 N4 -- , NUR0112 N02 , NUR0112 N12 , NUR0112 N22 , NUR0112 N32 , NUR0112 N42 WHERE 1=1 AND A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.NUT_DATE = :f_nut_date AND A.BLD_GUBUN = :f_bld_gubun AND A.MAGAM_SEQ = :f_magam_seq AND A.HO_DONG LIKE :f_ho_dong -- PRE NUT AND B.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE AND B.BUNHO (+)= A.BUNHO AND B.FKINP1001 (+)= A.FKINP1001 -- AND A0.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND A0.BUNHO = A.BUNHO -- 食事区分 AND N0.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE AND N0.NUR_GR_CODE (+)= A.DIRECT_GUBUN AND N0.NUR_MD_CODE (+)= DECODE(A.BLD_GUBUN , '1', A.JO_DIRECT_CODE , '2', A.JU_DIRECT_CODE , '3', A.SEOK_DIRECT_CODE ) AND N0.NUR_SO_CODE (+)= DECODE(A.BLD_GUBUN , '1', A.JO_DIRECT_CODE_D , '2', A.JU_DIRECT_CODE_D , '3', A.SEOK_DIRECT_CODE_D ) -- 食種 AND N1.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE AND N1.NUR_GR_CODE (+)= A.DIRECT_GUBUN AND N1.NUR_MD_CODE (+)= DECODE(A.BLD_GUBUN , '1', A.JO_DIRECT_CODE1 , '2', A.JU_DIRECT_CODE1 , '3', A.SEOK_DIRECT_CODE1 ) AND N1.NUR_SO_CODE (+)= DECODE(A.BLD_GUBUN , '1', A.JO_DIRECT_CODE1_D , '2', A.JU_DIRECT_CODE1_D , '3', A.SEOK_DIRECT_CODE1_D ) -- 主食 AND N2.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE AND N2.NUR_GR_CODE (+)= A.DIRECT_GUBUN AND N2.NUR_MD_CODE (+)= DECODE(A.BLD_GUBUN , '1', A.JO_DIRECT_CODE2 , '2', A.JU_DIRECT_CODE2 , '3', A.SEOK_DIRECT_CODE2 ) AND N2.NUR_SO_CODE (+)= DECODE(A.BLD_GUBUN , '1', A.JO_DIRECT_CODE2_D , '2', A.JU_DIRECT_CODE2_D , '3', A.SEOK_DIRECT_CODE2_D ) -- 副食 AND N3.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE AND N3.NUR_GR_CODE (+)= A.DIRECT_GUBUN AND N3.NUR_MD_CODE (+)= DECODE(A.BLD_GUBUN , '1', A.JO_DIRECT_CODE3 , '2', A.JU_DIRECT_CODE3 , '3', A.SEOK_DIRECT_CODE3 ) AND N3.NUR_SO_CODE (+)= DECODE(A.BLD_GUBUN , '1', A.JO_DIRECT_CODE3_D , '2', A.JU_DIRECT_CODE3_D , '3', A.SEOK_DIRECT_CODE3_D ) -- 飲料 AND N4.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE AND N4.NUR_GR_CODE (+)= A.DIRECT_GUBUN AND N4.NUR_MD_CODE (+)= '0305' AND N4.NUR_SO_CODE (+)= DECODE(A.BLD_GUBUN , '1', A.JO_NOMIMONO , '2', A.JU_NOMIMONO , '3', A.SEOK_NOMIMONO ) -- 食事区分 AND N02.HOSP_CODE (+)= B.HOSP_CODE AND N02.NUR_GR_CODE (+)= B.DIRECT_GUBUN AND N02.NUR_MD_CODE (+)= DECODE(:f_bld_gubun , '1', B.JO_DIRECT_CODE , '2', B.JU_DIRECT_CODE , '3', B.SEOK_DIRECT_CODE ) AND N02.NUR_SO_CODE (+)= DECODE(B.BLD_GUBUN , '1', B.JO_DIRECT_CODE_D , '2', B.JU_DIRECT_CODE_D , '3', B.SEOK_DIRECT_CODE_D ) -- 食種 AND N12.HOSP_CODE (+)= B.HOSP_CODE AND N12.NUR_GR_CODE (+)= B.DIRECT_GUBUN AND N12.NUR_MD_CODE (+)= DECODE(:f_bld_gubun , '1', B.JO_DIRECT_CODE1 , '2', B.JU_DIRECT_CODE1 , '3', B.SEOK_DIRECT_CODE1 ) AND N12.NUR_SO_CODE (+)= DECODE(:f_bld_gubun , '1', B.JO_DIRECT_CODE1_D , '2', B.JU_DIRECT_CODE1_D , '3', B.SEOK_DIRECT_CODE1_D ) -- 主食 AND N22.HOSP_CODE (+)= B.HOSP_CODE AND N22.NUR_GR_CODE (+)= B.DIRECT_GUBUN AND N22.NUR_MD_CODE (+)= DECODE(:f_bld_gubun , '1', B.JO_DIRECT_CODE2 , '2', B.JU_DIRECT_CODE2 , '3', B.SEOK_DIRECT_CODE2 ) AND N22.NUR_SO_CODE (+)= DECODE(:f_bld_gubun , '1', B.JO_DIRECT_CODE2_D , '2', B.JU_DIRECT_CODE2_D , '3', B.SEOK_DIRECT_CODE2_D ) -- 副食 AND N32.HOSP_CODE (+)= B.HOSP_CODE AND N32.NUR_GR_CODE (+)= B.DIRECT_GUBUN AND N32.NUR_MD_CODE (+)= DECODE(:f_bld_gubun , '1', B.JO_DIRECT_CODE3 , '2', B.JU_DIRECT_CODE3 , '3', B.SEOK_DIRECT_CODE3 ) AND N32.NUR_SO_CODE (+)= DECODE(:f_bld_gubun , '1', B.JO_DIRECT_CODE3_D , '2', B.JU_DIRECT_CODE3_D , '3', B.SEOK_DIRECT_CODE3_D ) -- 飲料 AND N42.HOSP_CODE (+)= B.HOSP_CODE AND N42.NUR_GR_CODE (+)= B.DIRECT_GUBUN AND N42.NUR_MD_CODE (+)= '0305' AND N42.NUR_SO_CODE (+)= DECODE(:f_bld_gubun , '1', B.JO_NOMIMONO , '2', B.JU_NOMIMONO , '3', B.SEOK_NOMIMONO ) UNION ALL SELECT
-- '3' AS TRANS_YN -- CANCEL '0' IP , '0' TI , '0' TN , '0' TR , '1' CA -- , B.HOSP_CODE AS HOSP_CODE , B.BUNHO AS BUNHO , A0.SUNAME AS SUNAME -- , TO_DATE(:f_nut_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AS NUT_DATE , :f_bld_gubun AS BLD_GUBUN -- , NULL AS TO_HO_DONG , NULL AS TO_HO_CODE -- , NULL AS TO_DIRECT_CODE_D , NULL AS TO_DIRECT_CODE1_D , NULL AS TO_DIRECT_CODE2_D , NULL AS TO_DIRECT_CODE3_D , NULL AS TO_NOMIMONO , NULL AS TO_KUMJISIK -- , TO_CHAR(B.NUT_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AS FROM_NUT_DATE , B.BLD_GUBUN AS FROM_BLD_GUBUN -- , B.HO_DONG FROM_HO_DONG , B.HO_CODE FROM_HO_CODE -- , N02.NUR_SO_NAME AS FROM_DIRECT_CODE_D , N12.NUR_SO_NAME AS FROM_DIRECT_CODE1_D , N22.NUR_SO_NAME AS FROM_DIRECT_CODE2_D , N32.NUR_SO_NAME AS FROM_DIRECT_CODE3_D , N42.NUR_SO_NAME AS FROM_NOMIMONO , CASE WHEN ( :f_bld_gubun = '1' ) THEN B.JO_KUMJISIK WHEN ( :f_bld_gubun = '2' ) THEN B.JU_KUMJISIK WHEN ( :f_bld_gubun = '3' ) THEN B.SEOK_KUMJISIK ELSE NULL END AS FROM_KUMJISIK -- --, A.* --, B.* FROM ( SELECT A.* FROM ( SELECT A.* FROM NUT2011 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.MAGAM_KEY < ( SELECT Z.MAGAM_KEY FROM NUT2011 Z WHERE Z.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND Z.NUT_DATE = :f_nut_date AND Z.BLD_GUBUN = :f_bld_gubun AND Z.MAGAM_SEQ = :f_magam_seq ) ORDER BY A.HOSP_CODE, A.MAGAM_KEY DESC ) A WHERE ROWNUM < 2 ) C , NUT2010 B -- , OUT0101 A0 -- , NUR0112 N02 , NUR0112 N12 , NUR0112 N22 , NUR0112 N32 , NUR0112 N42 WHERE 1=1 -- PRE NUT AND B.HOSP_CODE = C.HOSP_CODE AND B.NUT_DATE = C.NUT_DATE AND B.BLD_GUBUN = C.BLD_GUBUN AND B.MAGAM_SEQ = C.MAGAM_SEQ -- AND NOT EXISTS ( SELECT NULL FROM NUT2010 Z WHERE Z.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND Z.BUNHO = B.BUNHO AND Z.FKINP1001 = B.FKINP1001 AND Z.NUT_DATE = :f_nut_date AND Z.BLD_GUBUN = :f_bld_gubun AND Z.MAGAM_SEQ = :f_magam_seq AND Z.HO_DONG LIKE :f_ho_dong ) -- AND A0.HOSP_CODE = B.HOSP_CODE AND A0.BUNHO = B.BUNHO -- 食事区分 AND N02.HOSP_CODE (+)= B.HOSP_CODE AND N02.NUR_GR_CODE (+)= B.DIRECT_GUBUN AND N02.NUR_MD_CODE (+)= DECODE(:f_bld_gubun , '1', B.JO_DIRECT_CODE , '2', B.JU_DIRECT_CODE , '3', B.SEOK_DIRECT_CODE ) AND N02.NUR_SO_CODE (+)= DECODE(B.BLD_GUBUN , '1', B.JO_DIRECT_CODE_D , '2', B.JU_DIRECT_CODE_D , '3', B.SEOK_DIRECT_CODE_D ) -- 食種 AND N12.HOSP_CODE (+)= B.HOSP_CODE AND N12.NUR_GR_CODE (+)= B.DIRECT_GUBUN AND N12.NUR_MD_CODE (+)= DECODE(:f_bld_gubun , '1', B.JO_DIRECT_CODE1 , '2', B.JU_DIRECT_CODE1 , '3', B.SEOK_DIRECT_CODE1 ) AND N12.NUR_SO_CODE (+)= DECODE(:f_bld_gubun , '1', B.JO_DIRECT_CODE1_D , '2', B.JU_DIRECT_CODE1_D , '3', B.SEOK_DIRECT_CODE1_D ) -- 主食 AND N22.HOSP_CODE (+)= B.HOSP_CODE AND N22.NUR_GR_CODE (+)= B.DIRECT_GUBUN AND N22.NUR_MD_CODE (+)= DECODE(:f_bld_gubun , '1', B.JO_DIRECT_CODE2 , '2', B.JU_DIRECT_CODE2 , '3', B.SEOK_DIRECT_CODE2 ) AND N22.NUR_SO_CODE (+)= DECODE(:f_bld_gubun , '1', B.JO_DIRECT_CODE2_D , '2', B.JU_DIRECT_CODE2_D , '3', B.SEOK_DIRECT_CODE2_D ) -- 副食 AND N32.HOSP_CODE (+)= B.HOSP_CODE AND N32.NUR_GR_CODE (+)= B.DIRECT_GUBUN AND N32.NUR_MD_CODE (+)= DECODE(:f_bld_gubun , '1', B.JO_DIRECT_CODE3 , '2', B.JU_DIRECT_CODE3 , '3', B.SEOK_DIRECT_CODE3 ) AND N32.NUR_SO_CODE (+)= DECODE(:f_bld_gubun , '1', B.JO_DIRECT_CODE3_D , '2', B.JU_DIRECT_CODE3_D , '3', B.SEOK_DIRECT_CODE3_D ) -- 飲料 AND N42.HOSP_CODE (+)= B.HOSP_CODE AND N42.NUR_GR_CODE (+)= B.DIRECT_GUBUN AND N42.NUR_MD_CODE (+)= '0305' AND N42.NUR_SO_CODE (+)= DECODE(:f_bld_gubun , '1', B.JO_NOMIMONO , '2', B.JU_NOMIMONO , '3', B.SEOK_NOMIMONO ) ORDER BY 2 --A.HOSP_CODE , 7 --A.HO_DONG , 8 --A.HO_CODE
